                                                      PLACE

Growing plants indoors is an excellent choice if you have a limited budget.

                                                      EXPERIENCE

                                                      Always consider your level of cultivation expertise. If youâ€™re just getting started, start with autoflowering seeds because theyâ€™re simple to grow and virtually guarantee success.                                                       EFFECTS

                                                      If you desire high THC or high CBD levels, you should first take the strength of the seeds into account because there is often a trade-off between the two. So, high CBD seeds are your best bet if you want to use cannabis seeds for medical reasons.
